                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17940917-109-defend1358 t17940917-109-punish570"></join>
               Imprisoned six months in Newgate
            </rs>, and to find <rs id="t17940917-109-punish571" type="punishmentDescription">
