                     <interp inst="t17940917-109-punish571" type="punishmentSubcategory" value="sureties"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17940917-109-defend1358 t17940917-109-punish571"></join>
               security for twelve months
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the London Jury before Mr. COMMON SERGEANT.</p>
